Amendment to the UNITED NATIONS FEDERAL REPUBLIC OF YUGOSLAVIA (SERBIA AND
MONTENEGRO) REGULATIONS respecting measures to give effect to United
Nations Security Council Resolution 820 (1993) adopted on April 17, 1993,
strengthening transport, trade and financial sanctions and further expand
the scope of the existing trade embargo against the Federal Republic of
Yugoslavia (Serbia and Montenegro).
